      "title": "Trains from outstation areas to Colombo suspended",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The General Manager of Sri Lanka Railways says that trains from outstations to Colombo have been suspended due to the curfew.",
        "However, he said that trains departing from Colombo in the evening will function normally.",
        "Curfew has been imposed in the Colombo administrative district with effect from 12 noon today until 5.00 a.m. tomorrow (15)."
      ],
